My name is Angell Waters.  I have #128/9 on the dialog list on this site.  I am currently working on a self-produced documentary on the black experience in vietnam.  I would like anyone with anything to say on the subject to visit the site.  I am located in the Westchester area in New York and hope to have a few subjects for my documentary soon.  All men of color be they black, white, hispanic, Indiank etc. . . . are welcome to share individual view on the matter.<br>

